{{Infobox national volleyball team |name=Argentina |gender=women|type=U23 |image=Flag of Argentina.svg |image_border=yes |federation=Federación del Voleibol Argentino |website=[http://www.feva.org.ar www.feva.org.ar] |confederation=CSV |manager= |coach= |World Champs apps = 2 |World Champs first= 2013 |World Champs best = 10th Place : ([[2013 FIVB Volleyball Women's U23 World Championship|2013]]) |Regional name = [[Women's U22 South American Volleyball Championship|South America U22 Championship]] |Regional cup apps = 2 |Regional cup first = [[2014 Women's U22 South American Volleyball Championship|2014]] |Regional cup best = 4th Place : ([[2014 Women's U22 South American Volleyball Championship|2014]], [[2016 Women's U22 South American Volleyball Championship|2016]]). |pattern_b1=_3stripesonwhite|leftarm1=ffffff|body1=00ccff|rightarm1=ffffff|shorts1=ffffff| |pattern_b2=|leftarm2=002E63|body2=365194|rightarm2=002E63|shorts2=365194| |pattern_b3=_om1112H|leftarm3=00BFFF|body3=0033cc|rightarm3=00BFFF|shorts3=00B9FB| }}
The '''Argentina women's national under-23 volleyball team''' represents Argentina in [[women|women's]] under-23 volleyball Events, it is controlled and managed by the [[Federación Argentina de Voleibol|Argentinian Volleyball federation]] that is a member of [[South America]]n [[volleyball]] body [[Confederación Sudamericana de Voleibol]] '''(CSV)''' and the international [[volleyball]] body government the [[Federation Internationale de Volleyball]] '''(FIVB)'''.
