{{Orphan|date=November 2013}}

'''City Arena Tallinn''' is an outdoor [[arena]] for adventure in [[Tallinn]], [[Estonia]]. It's the largest of its kind in the Baltic states, the arena has {{convert|1400|m2|sqft|abbr=on}} for indoor activities. The arena has several adventure themes such as Spiderpark for climbing, Segtrack for [[Segways]] and Neon [[minigolf]].

In City Arena Tallinn is it possible to rent rooms for party and events.

The Arena is located in the centre of Tallinn, in [[Veerenni]] subdistrict, the address is Tatari 58.

